ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject2002-2003 - TRANSFER UNDISTRIBUTED BALANCES ** Wheat **
PrecisOrder authorising the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts as of December 31, 2009, by transferring the undistributed funds in the 2002-2003 pool accounts for wheat to a separate account; and (b) to pay to the persons who are entitled to receive payments the amount to which they are entitled out of the separate account.
